title: Tally | Tato and Tuto | 4
description:
When are arrests are finally made, it’s not who anyone expected. The FBI and local police seem to be zeroing in on a group of suspects. And soon, the King will have to make an important decision.

Can’t wait for Episode 5? It’s available now exclusively to Wondery+ subscribers. Go to wondery.com/plus 

“Where the Enemy Sleeps” is performed by Scott Mackay featuring Lucette.
